\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Zu2H4pN3aHlxZ_n32K_a3dctRio=/802x534/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/55OJXAFPEVFYXEOQRANZXDYIMQ.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FZu2H4pN3aHlxZ_n32K_a3dctRio%3D%2F802x534%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F55OJXAFPEVFYXEOQRANZXDYIMQ.JPG&h=495749f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n楊先生（左）認為，科興疫苗並不能給予他信心，而盧先生（右）則指，現時兩款疫苗的副作用頗多，故暫不會考慮打針。本報記者攝<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n政府力推「疫苗氣泡」大計，今日（15日）宣佈將疫苗接種計劃年齡下限調低至16歲或以上。不過絕大多數年輕人均向《蘋果》表示沒有意欲報名，認為疫苗的副作用令人擔憂。有市民更稱，即使疫苗或是開放外地旅遊的先決條件，亦無意接種，「去旅行緊要啲定命仔緊要啲？」<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210415/GR7DLKQHZRGV5KPLLKFBGHSSGI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210415%2FGR7DLKQHZRGV5KPLLKFBGHSSGI%2F&d=Uh5SjXth0XRRLWSKrhPNwC1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=422e37f2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210415%2FGR7DLKQHZRGV5KPLLKFBGHSSGI%2F&h=888f2064\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210415/GR7DLKQHZRGV5KPLLKFBGHSSGI/</a>"},{"pid":"cc968009cdec1fcf5faf73007007fe058bee7532","tid":2490243,"uid":86449,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T12:23:15.000Z","msg":"黃小姐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02e46132c4f507c112a2b77e62271c563c309c76","tid":2490243,"uid":55917,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T12:23:45.000Z","msg":"黃小姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cheerleading.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cheerleading.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cbe87cf7fe642f127ade12b73e6b3816b1fd88a","tid":2490243,"uid":79410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T12:24:08.000Z","msg":"黃小姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" c