f\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e32ca15009523d83004803ef6f6f51d3a33e7c7","tid":2490243,"uid":70964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d60728f80603deca6e2d87ce0be92935a1aec09c","tid":2490243,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T12:22:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/1PRvnMrqoKomb5Dq2FBBp_pfIGM=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OKQBIRG4NJHJFOMQUB7TIHV24Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F1PRvnMrqoKomb5Dq2FBBp_pfIGM%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOKQBIRG4NJHJFOMQUB7TIHV24Q.jpg&h=c8efd316&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雖然政府推出「疫苗氣泡」意圖吸引更多人打針，但有年輕人並不買賬，直言會照樣拒打。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/hl0b5tcD3xw6pATij86eizRQCtQ=/802x534/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SNN52U7NTNGQDGVWLPXDMCZKHM.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fhl0b5tcD3xw6pATij86eizRQCtQ%3D%2F802x534%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSNN52U7NTNGQDGVWLPXDMCZKHM.JPG&h=eefb5a34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n許同學（左）和楊同學（右）均稱，暫不考慮接種武肺疫苗。本報記者攝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/l4DOE7EvEtRFD2os0pXMsJ737qQ=/802x534/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4UTYJMQ5AJFODERBL4RLLMSZQE.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fl4DOE7EvEtRFD2os0pXMsJ737qQ%3D%2F802x534%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4UTYJMQ5AJFODERBL4RLLMSZQE.JPG&h=4ee278b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n19歲的黃小姐認為，疫苗的風險可能比成效更大。本報記者攝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Zu2H4pN3aHlxZ_n32K_a3dctRio=/802x534/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/55OJXAFPEVFYXEOQRANZXDYIMQ.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FZu2H4pN3aHlxZ_n32K_a3dctRio%3D%2F802x534%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F55OJXAFPEVFYXEOQRANZXDYIMQ.JPG&h=495749f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n楊先生（左）認為，科興疫苗並不能給予他信心，而盧先生（右）則指，現時兩款疫苗的副作用頗多，故暫不會考慮打針。本報記者攝<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n政府力推「疫苗氣泡」大計，今日（15日）宣佈將疫苗接種計劃年齡下限調低至16歲或以上。不過絕大多數年輕人均向《蘋果》表示沒有意欲報名，認為疫苗的副作用令人擔憂。有市民更稱，即使疫苗或是開放外地旅遊的先決條件，亦無意接種，「去旅行緊要啲定命仔緊要啲？」<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210415/GR7DLKQHZRGV5KPLLKFBGHSSGI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210415%2FGR7DLKQHZRGV5KPLLKFBGHSSGI%2F&d=Uh5SjXth0XRRLWSKrhPNwC1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=422e37f2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210415%2FGR7DLKQHZRGV5KPLLKFBGHSSGI%2F&h=888f2064\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210415/GR7DLKQHZRGV5KPLLKFBGHSSGI/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T12:26:51.000Z","msg":"黃小姐好<span class=\"red\">兇</span>恨"},{"pid":"0dd21c09f7f91429f2c0e447a9aad81d831083ec","tid":2490243,"uid":6238,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T12:26:59.000Z","msg":"睇到張封面圖就已經知討論既重點係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/crystalball.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ab39f1f382129b9dad8b5ea159308355e036205","tid":2490243,"uid":232005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T12:27:14.000Z","msg":"黃小姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f0fd27f7c7882b32f882658ff0c61fc9e16ece5","tid":2490243,"uid":373277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT